title: New Caledonia Employed Persons
description: The number of employed persons in New Caledonia increased to 67110 in the first quarter of 2022 from 64533 in the fourth quarter of 2021. Employed Persons in New Caledonia averaged 71042.21  from 1995 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 89489  in the third quarter of 2019 and a record low of 45986  in the first quarter of 1995. This page provides - New Caledonia Employed Persons - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: ISEE, New Caledonia
